casebody.data:
No. 10-6343 (10A267). Cal Coburn Brown, Petitioner v. Washington. 561 U.S. 1054, 131 S. Ct. 58,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1148,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5730. September 10, 2010.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Kennedy, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Superior Court of Washington, King County, denied.
